<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c4">[٤٧٩]</span> في <span class="c2">(أ)</span> ، <span class="c2">(ب)</span> : <span class="c2">(إذا)</span> .<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
